The '''Nixors''' were a race from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nixor/Legends|Nixor]] in the [[Nixor system/Legends|Nixor system]]. They were in a longstanding feud with the rest of the system during the early years of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The Nixors operated the decrepit [[Nixor Spaceport]].

